overview: Taking a cue from last fall's enormously successful DECADE OF DOMINANCE: Tennessee Football 90s, the Vol Network has produced an exciting special edition DVD version of this blockbuster hit. It's the first DVD in Vol Network history!  -Over 45 minutes of bonus footage including interviews as well as exclusive locker room speeches and celebrations.  -Bonus audio track featuring UT legends Gus Manning and Haywood Harris.  -Interactive menus  -All-American Gallery  -1990s Results  -First DVD in Vol Network History!
title: TN Vols - Decade of Dominance
